==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Bigoted
<hw>Big"ot*ed</hw>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Obstinately and blindly attached
to some creed, opinion practice, or ritual; unreasonably devoted to a
system or party, and illiberal toward the opinions of others.</def>
⟦ldquo⟧<xex>Bigoted</xex> to strife.⟦rdquo⟧ <rj><au>Byron.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><syn><b>Syn.</b> -- Prejudiced; intolerant; narrow-minded.</syn>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Bigotedly</ent>⟦br⟧
